<paragraph blockId="10.[151,703,1485,1545]" box="[151,337,1520,1545]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,288,1520,1545]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 42" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1775,1797]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,194,1753]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[151,1436,193,1754]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 42. Species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD 23 – 24. A. praestigiosa. 25 – 26. A. johannismarci. 27 – 28. A. brevignoni sp. nov. holotype. 29 – 30. A. rameli. 31 – 34. A. willmotti sp. nov.. 31 – 32. Male holotye. 33 – 34. Female allotype. 35 – 38. A. iracyi. 35 – 36. Male. 37 – 38. Female. 39 – 42. A. saulensis tunari comb. nov. 39 – 40. Male. 41 – 42. Female. Scale bar = 1 cm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233290/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">
Figs 
<number box="[215,288,1520,1544]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="23.78" valueMax="24.56" valueMin="23.0">23–24</number>
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[299,328,1520,1545]" captionStart="FIGURES 56 – 62" captionStartId="11.[151,264,1346,1368]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,267,1324]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[151,1436,267,1324]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIGURES 56 – 62. Male genitalia of species of Argyrogrammana collected at the PNSD. 56. A. praestigiosa. 57. A. johannismarci. 58. A. brevignoni sp. nov. holotype. 59. A. rameli. 60. A. willmotti sp. nov. holotype. 61. A. iracyi. 62. A. saulensis tunari comb. nov. Left to right: dorsal view of uncus, lateral view of tegumen, saccus, uncus, gnathos, valva and aedeagus, and ventral view of valva. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233293/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">56</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,1592,2013]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">
Only one specimen was collected at 
<collectionCode box="[562,633,1592,1616]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">PNSD</collectionCode>
in 
<number box="[670,726,1592,1616]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="2014.0">2014</number>
while it was flying and resting on the underside of a leaf about four meters from the ground around 
<number box="[560,588,1628,1653]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="13.0">13</number>
:00h.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1436,1592,2013]" lastBlockId="11.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="238" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">
Previously, this species was recorded only in 
<collectingCountry box="[730,898,1664,1689]" name="French Guiana" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Brevignon" box="[916,1231,1664,1689]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Brevignon, C. &amp; Gallard, J. - Y. (1995) Contribuition a l'etude des Riodinidae de Guyane Francaise. Le genre Argyrogrammana Strand, 1932. Lambillionea, 95, 393 - 406." type="journal article" year="1995">
Brévignon &amp; Gallard 
<number box="[1172,1231,1664,1689]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="1995.0">1995</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Hall" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Hall, J. P. W. &amp; Willmott, K. R. (1995) Notes on the genus Argyrogrammana, with descriptions of five new species (Lepidoptera: Riodinidae). Tropical Lepidoptera, 6, 136 - 143." type="journal article" year="1995">
Hall &amp; Willmott 
<number box="[151,208,1700,1725]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="1995.0">1995</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and the present record is the first one to 
<collectingCountry box="[680,752,1700,1725]" name="Brazil" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[763,1107,1700,1724]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="praestigiosa">
<emphasis box="[763,1107,1700,1724]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">Argyrogrammana praestigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="P. Jauffret &amp; Martins, 2006" authorityName="P. Jauffret &amp; Martins" authorityYear="2006" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sonazul">
<emphasis box="[1318,1435,1700,1725]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. sonazul</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jauffret" box="[151,462,1736,1761]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Jauffret, P. &amp; Martins, A. L. (2006) Description de trois especes nouvelles de Riodinidae provenant de la region de l'embouchure de l'amazone (Para, Bresil) (Lepidoptera). Lambillionea, 106, 395 - 401." type="journal article" year="2006">
P. Jauffret &amp; Martins, 
<number box="[403,462,1736,1761]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="2006.0">2006</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, a species described based on a single male from Santo Antônio do Tauá, Pará, 
<collectingCountry box="[1368,1436,1736,1761]" name="Brazil" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Jauffret" box="[158,434,1772,1797]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Jauffret, P. &amp; Martins, A. L. (2006) Description de trois especes nouvelles de Riodinidae provenant de la region de l'embouchure de l'amazone (Para, Bresil) (Lepidoptera). Lambillionea, 106, 395 - 401." type="journal article" year="2006">
Jauffret &amp; Martins 
<number box="[373,434,1772,1797]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="2006.0">2006</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). The taxonomic status of 
<taxonomicName box="[726,842,1772,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sonazul">
<emphasis box="[726,842,1772,1797]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. sonazul</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a distinct species, a synonym or even a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName box="[187,363,1809,1832]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="praestigiosa">
<emphasis box="[187,363,1809,1832]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. praestigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is uncertain since no other specimen is known for this species and the genitalia was not illustrated on its original description. The specimen of 
<taxonomicName box="[767,938,1844,1868]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="praestigiosa">
<emphasis box="[767,938,1844,1868]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. praestigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
collected in 
<collectionCode box="[1082,1153,1844,1868]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">PNSD</collectionCode>
has the blue patch of the forewing upperside with the anterior and posterior elements shared with both 
<typeStatus box="[1070,1129,1881,1905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">types</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName box="[1174,1348,1881,1904]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="praestigiosa">
<emphasis box="[1174,1348,1881,1904]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. praestigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sonazul">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. sonazul</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, suggesting that the latter might be co-specific with the former. Despite the distribution of 
<taxonomicName box="[1259,1429,1916,1940]" class="Insecta" family="Lycaenidae" genus="Argyrogrammana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="praestigiosa">
<emphasis box="[1259,1429,1916,1940]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">A. praestigiosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the genitalia of the specimen from 
<collectionCode box="[543,614,1952,1976]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">PNSD</collectionCode>
is similar to that illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Brevignon" box="[966,1374,1952,1977]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Brevignon, C. &amp; Gallard, J. - Y. (1995) Contribuition a l'etude des Riodinidae de Guyane Francaise. Le genre Argyrogrammana Strand, 1932. Lambillionea, 95, 393 - 406." type="journal article" year="1995">
Brévignon &amp; Gallard (
<number box="[1220,1279,1952,1977]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="1995.0">1995</number>
, fig. 
<number box="[1337,1366,1952,1976]" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" value="10.0">10</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[151,320,1988,2013]" name="French Guiana" pageId="10" pageNumber="237">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
, differing only by the presence of a median membranous area in valva, not illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Brevignon" lastPageId="11" lastPageNumber="238" pageId="10" pageNumber="237" refString="Brevignon, C. &amp; Gallard, J. - Y. (1995) Contribuition a l'etude des Riodinidae de Guyane Francaise. Le genre Argyrogrammana Strand, 1932. Lambillionea, 95, 393 - 406." type="journal article" year="1995">
Brévignon &amp; Gallard (
<number box="[281,341,151,176]" pageId="11" pageNumber="238" value="1995.0">1995</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, and the projection of the distal margin of the valva slightly projecting dorsally in the specimen from 
<collectingCountry box="[212,382,188,213]" name="French Guiana" pageId="11" pageNumber="238">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
